  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd-\u0ba4\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd-\u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd-\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd-\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf-\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd/175-303014",
  "time_ut": 1661454491,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "War can happen in cyber space too: President Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the future war may take place not only on land, air and sea but also in cyber space. Therefore, President Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that our soldiers should have the necessary knowledge for such a technical war.",
        "Pointing out that discipline, training and knowledge are necessary to build a successful army, the President said that the Sir John Kothalawala Defense University is already fulfilling all these things.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe said the above yesterday afternoon (25) when he attended the presentation ceremony of President's Color and University Color to General Sir John Kothalawala Defense University.",
        "The President noted that this university is not limited to the military and civilian students from countries with fewer universities are also enrolled in it. (a)"
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Ranil",
          "label": "PERSON"
